steps.step: {"blocks":[{"key":"a9ebi","text":"Scan midbrain section using the Pannoramic Midi II FL, HQ Scientific 60x","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
{"blocks":[{"key":"bs5l9","text":"Click on Adjust canvas size and adjust it at 1596x1198","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"4kkl7","text":"With the free hand selections tool, draft a neuromelanin-pigmented neuron (excluding the nucleus) and measure the optical density (pixel brightness) and the area","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"brp24","text":"With the free hand selections tool, draft the neuromelanin pigment of the neuron and measure the optical density (pixel brightness) and the area","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"f3b2r","text":"With the free hand selections tool, draft 15-25 non-pigmented neurons (excluding the nucleus), measure the optical density and calculate the mean value","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"4vo9d","text":"Normalize (i.e., substract) the values of the neuromelanin-pigmented neuron’s optical density with the mean value of the optical density of the non-pigmented neurons","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"3kf8e","text":"Extra measurement: calculate the percentage of the neuronal area occupied by the pigment diving the neuromelanin pigment area by the neuron’s area","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
